rows.label: qst702504_msg0002
rows.name: What on earth is going on?

rows.label: qst702504_msg0003
rows.name:
Why are Liberalitas monsters here?
Is the ecosystem out of whack?

rows.label: qst702504_msg0004
rows.name:
Not far off, maybe. With
the Heaven's Holy Grail
rampaging everywhere...

rows.label: qst702504_msg0005
rows.name:
Monsters driven from their homes cause
territorial disputes in new lands, and then
more monsters are driven from their homes.

rows.label: qst702504_msg0006
rows.name:
So... Iiran monsters lost their homes
and flowed into Liberalitas...

rows.label: qst702504_msg0007
rows.name:
And as a result, monsters from
there are flowing in here...?

rows.label: qst702504_msg0008
rows.name:
It is true that this area
approaches Liberalitas at this
time of year. It makes sense.

rows.label: qst702504_msg0009
rows.name:
We're not the only ones who
lose our homes in war...

rows.label: qst702504_msg0010
rows.name:
If the monster attacks continue, not
only Metsu, but every country will
need to strengthen their defenses.

rows.label: qst702504_msg0011
rows.name: ...We have less time than I thought.

rows.label: qst702504_msg0013
rows.name:
I'm sorry, more monsters!
They're inside this time!

rows.label: qst702504_msg0014
rows.name: Tch, no rest for the weary.

rows.label: qst702504_msg0015
rows.name:
But we've thinned their numbers.
They should be at their limit soon.
